<HEADLINE> Harbin Ready for Asian Winter Games </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HARBIN, Northern China, January 8 (Xinhua/OANA) -- The
competing sits for the third Asian Winter Games have been
completed and approved by the International Skiing Federation
(ISF), according to the organizers here on Monday.
</P>
<P>
