skiing, alpine skiing and ski jump are all ready for the eight day
event slated through February 4 to 10.
</P>
<P>
Electronic timers and five large screens have been installed in
both indoor and outdoor competing arenas.
</P>
<P>
About 470 referees and technique supervisors, 53 of them are
from outside China, will take the judging jobs during the
continental winter sports festival.
</P>
<P>
