in 1970 and Master of Arts in Law and Diplomacy in 1971 from the
Fletcher School of Law and Diplomacy, Tufts University,
Massachusetts, USA. He specialized in development economics,
comparative politics, and international organizations and legal
systems.
</P>
<P>
