Against the German mark, the Australian dollar ended at 1.0772
mark stronger from 1.0704 mark last Friday.
</P>
<P>
On the local financial market, the US dollar also made its
gains against the Japanese yen, ending at 105.41 yen from 104.65
yen last weekend.  
