install fire-protecting systems to reduce property losses, which
they had largely ignored previously, the report said.
</P>
<P>
Thailand's existing regulations do not provide for the standard
of fire-safety products and systems to be applied in buildings.
Some irresponsible developers have just installed poor equipment
in buildings.
</P>
<P>
Local analysts said that there are good signs owners of old
buildings intend to revise their fire-alarm and extinguishing
systems in future.  
