wages, he said.
</P>
<P>
Employers are to be allowed to hire illegal immigrants for
certain labor-intensive jobs in the border provinces on condition
they deposit a cash guarantee with police.
</P>
<P>
A Labor Ministry source said there are about 500,000 illegal
foreign laborers in the country, mostly from Myanmar,
</P>
<P>
