<HEADLINE> ACWF Official Meets Guest of Myanmar </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, January 8 (Xinhua) -- Huang Qizao, vice-chairman of
Executive Committee of All China Women's Federation (ACWF) met
with Daw Kyaing Kyaing, wife of Senior General Than Shwe of
Myanmar, here this morning.
</P>
<P>
They held cordial talks over the cause for women and children
as well as the long-standing friendly relations between the two
nations.
</P>
<P>
It is learned that a Chinese women's delegation visited Myanmar
last February, the first sent by ACWF since the establishment of
diplomatic relations between the two countries in 1950.
</P>
<P>
Daw is accompanying Than Shwe, chairman of the State Law and
Order Restoration Council of the Union of Myanmar, on a current
China tour. 
</P>
